    "attributes": {
        "action": "Push for the development of a 'green drugs' grading system for perscribers",
        "additional_details": "Many scientists believe it is crucial to act now, before issues worsen, particularly as many of these consequences remain\u202funknown, and may have future catastrophic effects on wildlife and biodiversity.\u202f \r\n\r\nSign this petition to push for development of a database to enable UK doctors to be able to access a database , allowing them to choose the most environmentally friendly drug option when prescribing medication to patients.",
        "background": "Pharmaceutical drugs in the\u202fenvironment is recognised as one of the top issues of global conservation concern.\u202fThe cocktail of medicines leaching into British waterways are\u202freported to cause\u202fharmful effects on wildlife, as compounds leach into their tissues;many are exposed for their whole lives.",
